## 🎯 Common Use Cases

### **Get All Patients (Dashboard)**
```javascript
import { getAllPatients } from '../data/mockData';

// Async with simulated delay (300ms)
const data = await getAllPatients();
console.log(data.patients); // Array of 4 patients
```

---

### **Get One Patient (Detail View)**
```javascript
import { getPatientWithDetails } from '../data/mockData';

// Async with simulated delay (300ms)
const patient = await getPatientWithDetails('pat_001');
console.log(patient.name); // "Sarah Martinez"
console.log(patient.cms_485.supplies); // Array of 6 supplies
```

