## 🎨 Demo Flow Example

**Full user journey in code:**

```javascript
// 1. Load dashboard
const { patients } = await getAllPatients();
// Shows: Sarah, Robert, Mary, John

// 2. User clicks on Mary Johnson (Ready to Order)
const mary = await getPatientWithDetails('pat_003');
// Shows: Full details, 5 supplies, doctor signed ✓

// 3. User clicks "Approve & Order Supplies"
const newOrder = await createMockSupplyOrder('pat_003');
// Returns: New order with tracking number

// 4. User views tracking
const tracking = getTrackingTimeline(newOrder.id);
// Shows: Timeline with 4 steps
```

