## ⚠️ Important Notes

### **For Demo Day:**

1. **No API calls needed** - All data is local
2. **Instant loading** - Or use built-in delay() function
3. **Predictable** - Same data every time
4. **No internet required** - Works offline

### **Pre-load Data:**
```javascript
// In App.jsx or main.jsx
import { mockPatients } from './data/mockData';

// Store in React Context or state on app load
const [patients] = useState(mockPatients);
```

### **Error Handling:**
```javascript
// All get functions return null if not found
const patient = getPatientDetail('pat_999'); // null
if (!patient) {
  // Show error or redirect
}
```

